The following steps must be followed in order to properly set up the server.

---[ Files

store/database/

store/certificate/ca.crt
store/certificate/server.crt

store/code/server.cod

store/database/database.yml

store/key/server.key

---[ Scripts

server/server.py

---[ Packages

packages/ktc.py -> server/ktc.py
env.py (one from the same environment as the server's)

---[ Suites

les suites de tests doivent etre dans un repertoire genre suites/ donc
etre copiees sur le server.
